OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOvernight
OL,6,Funder clear skies the temperature will
OL,7,Ffall close to freezing with frost
OL,8,Fpatches possible. The light winds
OL,9,Fcould also give rise to some fog
OL,10,Fpatches forming.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FPatchy cloud and sunny
OL,13,Fspells expected, light winds continue
OL,14,Fbut breezy along the coast. Fog and
OL,15,Flow cloud developing Wednesday night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
