OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FThursday, cloudy with a weakening band
OL,7,Fof rain moving slowly eastwards. Sunny
OL,8,Fspells expected Friday. Turning cloudy
OL,9,Fwith patchy rain and drizzle on
OL,10,FSaturday.
